Privacy Policy for Idle Tycoon: Business Empire
Last Updated: July 19, 2025

1. Introduction

Thank you for playing Idle Tycoon: Business Empire ("the Game"). This Privacy Policy describes how we collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use our mobile application.

Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. By downloading, installing, or playing the Game, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

a) Information Collected Automatically

Gameplay Data: We collect and store your game progress locally on your device. This includes your cash, businesses owned, upgrades purchased, achievements unlocked, investments, and other game state data. This is necessary to save your progress.

Device and Usage Information: We may collect information about your device, such as the device model, operating system version, advertising ID (IDFA for iOS / GAID for Android), IP address, and other unique identifiers. We also collect data about how you interact with the Game, such as your session duration, features used, and in-game events.

b) Information You Provide to Us

Player Name: You have the option to set a player name in the Game. This name is stored locally on your device.

c) Information from Third-Party Partners

We may use third-party services for advertising and analytics. These partners may collect information automatically from your device. This may include:

Advertising Partners: To serve advertisements in the Game, our partners may collect your advertising ID and other device information to show you ads that are more relevant to your interests. [Example: Google AdMob, Unity Ads, etc.]

Analytics Partners: To understand how our players interact with the Game and to improve its performance, our analytics partners may collect usage and device data. [Example: Google Analytics for Firebase, Unity Analytics, etc.]

Please review the privacy policies of our third-party partners to understand their data collection practices.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To Provide and Operate the Game: To save your game progress, manage game state, and deliver the core features of the app.

To Improve and Optimize the Game: To analyze player behavior, identify and fix bugs, and enhance the overall player experience.

To Serve Advertisements: To display third-party advertisements within the Game. This may include personalized or interest-based advertising.

To Comply with Legal Obligations: To enforce our terms of service and to comply with legal and regulatory requirements.

4. Data Storage

Your core game progress (cash, businesses, upgrades, etc.) is stored locally on your device using your device's internal storage. We do not store this personal game progress on our servers. Data collected by third-party services (like analytics or ad networks) is stored on their respective servers.

5. Your Rights and Choices

Opt-out of Interest-Based Advertising: You can opt out of personalized advertising by adjusting the settings on your mobile device.

On Android: Navigate to Settings > Google > Ads and enable "Opt out of Ads Personalization."

On iOS: Navigate to Settings > Privacy > Advertising and enable "Limit Ad Tracking."

Resetting Game Data: You can clear all locally stored game data by uninstalling the Game or clearing the app's data through your device's settings. Please note that this action is irreversible and will erase all your game progress.

6. Children's Privacy

Our Game is not directed to children under the age of 13 (or the relevant age in your jurisdiction), and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us at [aasifaalamkhan@gmail.com], and we will take steps to delete such information.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy within the Game or on our website. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

[aasifaalamkhan@gmail.com]

